As of 2025, Brno Zidenice to Brno hlavni (2.6km) is frequent southbound, but only if one includes reservation-only Praha-Wien RegioJet trains for which it's apparently not possible to buy a ticket for that segment (though one could probably buy a ticket for a longer segment and get off early)
